    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2>-较前作更开阔的冒险方式，在随机生成的大地图中自由探索<br><br>-主副职业系统构成了生物可学习的技能池，更灵活的技能搭配方式<br>-大量的普通和传奇宝石，构成更有深度的装备系统<br>-每通关一个难度都会解锁新的地图设施，保持攻关的新鲜感<br>-大量的生物，技能，物品，设施，几倍于前作的内容量<br>-支持创意工坊，并维持前作简洁灵活的MOD制作方式<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/7b9cb90d65732891fc0ff7f5422aaa1c.poster.avif?t=1726281733\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/7b9cb90d65732891fc0ff7f5422aaa1c.webm?t=1726281733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/7b9cb90d65732891fc0ff7f5422aaa1c.mp4?t=1726281733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在随机生成的世界自由探索</h2>广袤的大地图，大量的随机事件和丰富的功能性设施，让玩家在每局随机生成的地图上自由地进行探索，在充满随机性和奇遇的世界中完成自己的独特冒险。<br>合理地规划路线，权衡探索所带来的利弊，与无处不在的瘴气斗智斗勇，在有限的时间内击败魔王。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/02453998be62149d3ce6711aec51431b.poster.avif?t=1726281733\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/02453998be62149d3ce6711aec51431b.webm?t=1726281733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/02453998be62149d3ce6711aec51431b.mp4?t=1726281733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁数十种生物，征服魔王仆从</h2>数十种极具特色、形象鲜明的传奇生物，可供玩家收集、解锁、培养，打造独属于自己的传奇生物军团。<br>这些生物被归类为：<br>战士/坦克/射手/刺客/法师/辅助，6大基础职业。<br>剑士/肉山/弩手/忍者/火法/萨满等等，24种进阶职业。<br>除此之外，挑战随机出现的魔王，将其击败后可招致麾下，成为你独一无二的魔王仆从。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/2ba7142007966d0c4d4842c16e017933.poster.avif?t=1726281733\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/2ba7142007966d0c4d4842c16e017933.webm?t=1726281733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/2ba7142007966d0c4d4842c16e017933.mp4?t=1726281733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成长路径千变万化，每一步都重要</h2>200+技能可供学习，搭配每个生物拥有的专属技能，使用不同的技能搭配，可塑造不同风格的战斗方式。<br>通过不同方式获取的神徽，可提供数十种强大的增益，武装你的队伍，甚至决定你的BD走向。<br>丰富的装备词缀和消耗性道具，天降神雷或是全屏回血，召唤神兽或是叠加Buff，均可让你在战斗过程中如虎添翼，甚至逆风翻盘。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/9fe30410560a94202126be768b7d65ef.poster.avif?t=1726281733\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/9fe30410560a94202126be768b7d65ef.webm?t=1726281733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/9fe30410560a94202126be768b7d65ef.mp4?t=1726281733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >保留系列特色，游戏体验一脉相承</h2>古朴的美术风格更凸显每一种生物的特点，紧凑的战斗直击爽点。交互与探索方式简洁明了不花俏。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/b3d73d4ebdc7855124c185a542416b36.poster.avif?t=1726281733\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/b3d73d4ebdc7855124c185a542416b36.webm?t=1726281733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/b3d73d4ebdc7855124c185a542416b36.mp4?t=1726281733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>欢迎广大玩家加入官方测试群：580526571<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/7414a393681b2b354f66a21f891a1336.poster.avif?t=1726281733\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/7414a393681b2b354f66a21f891a1336.webm?t=1726281733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233790/extras/7414a393681b2b354f66a21f891a1336.mp4?t=1726281733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
